# collar — skills

> Complex tasks saved as skills. Stale skills patched. Workflows captured.

---

### Entity: skills

Complex→ Task:save(11) | Error:patch(11) | Workflow:captur(11)
Stale→ Skill:patch(11) | Outdated:fix(11) | Liable:update(11)

```yaml
entity: skills
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
    default: skills
states: [active]
lifecycle: active
```